{"tid":1692421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你想香港贏 - 定係 - 想要幾萬蚊？","createTime":"2019-11-04T05:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T04:39:38.000Z","uid":299171,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6e7484d7880ce40552edd1624710aa29ff2141","tid":1692421,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Powkdkd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPowkdkd.png&h=57171405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">罷一個月港共必跪</span></strong><br />\n你見港共政虎依家寧願假宵禁，都唔敢真正宵禁，就知佢依賴我哋返工嚟供養佢，無咗我哋唔得，而且係停一陣都唔得嗰隻。若然<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真 &middot; 三罷</span></strong>，根本個幾禮拜，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾盡一個月佢就跪低</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">儲夠三個月生活費即可罷</span></strong><br />\n若然罷，罷一個月贏撚硬。有咩資格先可以講罷工？其實就只不過係幾個月嘅生活費。 你有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三個月零收入仍然能夠生存</span></strong>嘅能力嘅話，其實就已經可以罷工。三個月零收入仍然生存，我覺得<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好多人都得，爭在肯唔肯</span></strong>。 清一次袋啫，又唔係叫你擋子彈，咁都唔肯？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我已準備好清袋，隨時罷得</span></strong><br />\n利申：小弟都要交租都要俾家用，但平時有正常儲蓄習慣，即使聽日起完全零收入仍可維持4至6個月，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我深信4至6個月夠贏有凸。已做好清袋嘅心理準備</strong></span>，隨時可以開始裸罷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">邊個跟隊？</span></strong><br />\n2015港股大時代我已經清過一次袋，而家咪又一條好漢，又唔使死。為咗今次，我唔介意清多一次。 我想知有幾多人同我一樣<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">有能力三個月零收入仍可生存</span></strong>。又或者<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">本身諗著轉工 / 唔做嘢一排唞一唞 </span></strong>。大家<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">喺度講定</span></strong>，曬定馬先，見人多咪大家唔淆囉。 夠人嘅話就搵文宣做宣傳，揀個日子一齊為香港清次袋。"},{"pid":"b005aa7c3e642b3bead3b36c54b87a2ed3d9e2ba","tid":1692421,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e02ae8fd6ece2c94d9b7e72e7f1a5c61b3cbf394","tid":1692421,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b005aa7c3e642b3bead3b36c54b87a2ed3d9e2ba","tid":1692421,"uid":258598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71029e0bb8088efa353151f2d5e372444ff8cd01","tid":1692421,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:25:01.000Z","msg":"無野阻到我返工<br />\n<br />\n-代香港人答你"},{"pid":"c3f602c32eccee215b7202f528afe3047697c464","tid":1692421,"uid":337336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:25:48.000Z","msg":"唔值得為呢個政權呢個民族賣命，攬炒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bba801c4feadeae76de1349d2222a4d2f4451af","tid":1692421,"uid":12864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"我願意"},{"pid":"b3e3d51c076909586921fac17e1b3317d1ee404c","tid":1692421,"uid":278858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"一定唔會有人罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}